        "id": "psb_1778046115668_4etpa76j",
        "label": "mountain breaking",
        "text": "The camera drives forward in a slow, deliberate push toward the mountain’s कठोर face, where cold stone bears deep fracture lines, and the air tightens with a dry mineral bite as faint vibrations pulse through the ground. Hairline cracks creep across the rock like living veins, dust lifting in tight spirals as the wind sharpens and cuts through the valleys at a slanted force, pressing against the terrain while a low, heavy rumble builds from within.\n\nA vast shadow sweeps across the mountain, swallowing light as the gada tears into the frame at immense speed, its descent ripping through dense air and forcing it aside with a deep, pressure-heavy roar that intensifies as it falls.\n\nThe moment of impact detonates with crushing force—the gada slams into the mountain and releases a violent shockwave that blasts outward, splitting stone, tearing massive slabs free, and hurling fragments into the air as a dense, choking dust cloud erupts upward, swallowing light while the ground convulses violently.\n\nCracks surge outward in all directions, racing across the mountain surface as entire sections collapse under their own weight, massive boulders breaking loose and crashing downward, colliding with explosive force that sends shards and debris scattering through the air.\n\nThe dust cloud expands like a heavy, breathing mass, rolling outward and veiling the shattered landscape while smaller rocks continue to fall in uneven rhythms, the ground’s violent trembling fading into deep residual pulses as the echo of impact travels across distant peaks and dissolves into a vast, weighted silence."
